      <title>红海袭击抬高价格，英国通胀担忧卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-inflation-worries-back-with-signs-red-sea-attacks-lift-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国私营企业报告称，由于该地区的冲突可能重新引发通货膨胀，成本出现五个月以来最大幅度的上涨，并且红海的货物运输受到干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/uk-inflation-worries-back-with-signs-red-sea-attacks-lift-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
